pageProduct.name: U By Kotex Designer Series Ultrathins Pads Wing Regular 22 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Don't let your period dull your sparkle with the U By Kotex® Designer series. Inspired by the latest trends, the designs feature a mix of prints and bold colours. The Rapid-Dry Core and unique 3-layer design will keep you feeling dry and comfortable, plus they are ultra thin and flexible so you'll feel like you're wearing nothing at all! Be protected in style!

  • With a Rapid-Dry Core that draws moisture away for faster absorption
  • With a range of different colour designs printed on the pads that are inspired by the latest trends.
  • With grooves that channel moisture into the centre of the pads, giving you even more protection from leaks
  • With secure wings to help keep the pad firmly in place
  • Perfect for medium flow days during your period.

U by Kotex® Designer Series Ultrathins with a 3D Rapid-Dry Core.

Size: 22 Pack
